                <a target="_blank" href="/Content/Remotely-Linux.zip">Linux x64 Files Only</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Install:</strong>
                <br />
                <span class="label label-default code">sudo [path]/Install-Ubuntu-x64.sh</span>
